               <p>First London Jury, before Mr. Sergeant Arabin.</p>
               <p>1189. 
               
                  <persName id="t18310512-199-defend1444" type="defendantName">
                     JOHN ANTHONY 
                     DOBBS
                  <interp inst="t18310512-199-defend1444" type="surname" value="DOBBS"></interp>
